<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038150" n="1"/>
<opener><salute><lb/>Viro <abbr>pl.</abbr> Reverendo ac Celeberrimo
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs>
  <lb/><rs type="person"><abbr>N.B.</abbr></rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quanquam amicitia nostra non <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimanda est ex frequentia
  <lb/>litterarum nostrarum, tamen nolui <add>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittere</add> ut diutius expect<add>ares</add> respon<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>sionem meam ad <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> tuas gratissimas, quas <date>mense Junio
  <lb/>superioris anni</date> accepi, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quia me nunc plures, quam
  <lb/>hactenus, caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad scribendum impellunt. <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>quum enim esse
  <lb/>duxi, ut Tibi significarem, me sub <date>initi<add>um</add> hujus anni</date> misisse
  <lb/>ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs> <rs type="biblio">Tentamen solutionis generalis Problematis traje<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <lb break="no"/>ctoriarum</rs>, ut si dignum judicaret <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2879139">Lipsiam</rs> transmitteret<choice><orig>,</orig><reg>.</reg></choice>
  <lb/>In isto Schediasmate modeste monui, quid in <rs type="biblio">Solutione</rs> tua
  <lb/>generali, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <date>mense Julio superioris <add>a</add>nni</date> <rs type="biblio">Actis</rs> inserta est,
  <lb/>desiderem, rogavique ut errorem, quem in <del/>regulam <add>T</add>uam
  <lb/><del/>irrepsisse <del/><add>credo</add>, corrigeres aut ejusdem <add>regul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> sensum plenius expli<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>cares. Te autem petitionem meam jam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>venisse suspicor ex <add>h</add>is
  <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> nuper ex <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> aliqua Tua excerpta transmi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>sit, verbis Tuis: <cit type="long"><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>trajectori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per quadraturas in transcendentibus
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>generaliter describi non possunt, et ego modum demum inveni qui
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ad dissimiles curvas transcendentes <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac similes sese extendit,
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>cujus specimen dedi in eadem scheda qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <rs type="biblio">Actis</rs> hujus mensis <date>Ja<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <lb break="no"/>nuarii</date> comparebit.<choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></quote></cit> Rogabo igitur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs>,<del/> ut script<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>meum Tecum, si fieri possit, co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicandum curet antequam
  <lb/>imprimatur, ut id, si nihil scitu dignum<del/> illud continere
  <lb/>reperias, supprimas omnino, aut saltem illi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> monenda
  <pb facs="1038151" n="2"/>
  <lb/>habebis, adjungas. Ceterum gaudeo, quod nunc agnoscas, Tra<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>jectorias per quadraturas in transcendentibus generaliter descri<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>bi non posse; sed rectius dixisses, si omisisses verba h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c<del/>
  <lb/><hi rend="u">in transcendentibus</hi>, nam meo quidem judicio<del/> in <hi rend="u">alge<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>braicis</hi> quoque trajectori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> generaliter per quadraturas
  <lb/>describi nequeunt. Rogo autem, ut omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in hanc rem
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me dicta sunt, boni consules.</p>
  <p rend="space">Vidi <rs type="person">Offenburgii</rs> <rs type="biblio">Schediasma</rs>
  <lb/>quo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> pulchre depexuit; sed puto me hu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>jus <add>r</add>ei poenam ferre;<del/> nebulo enim iste, me forte <rs type="person">Offen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>burgium</rs> esse judicans, contra me sub persona <hi rend="u"><rs type="person">Caroli Bal<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <lb break="no"/>di</rs></hi> in lucem protrusit <rs type="biblio">libellum</rs> famosum duabus plagu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>lis constantem, simillimum illius qu<add>em</add> contra Te edidit, ple<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>num contumeliis, ineptiis et paralogismis <add>ultra mod<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><del/> enormibus,</add> quem autem
    <lb/>Tuum exemplum secutus<del/> responsione nulla, nisi
  <lb/>necessitate coactus, dignabor. Plura sunt qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi persua<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>dent, ut credam <add>non</add> alium quam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzaliam</rs> hujus <rs type="biblio">libelli</rs> Aucto<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>rem esse, ea autem recensere non opus est. An <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzalia</rs> Pro<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>blemata duo ab <rs type="person">Offenburgio</rs> proposita soluturus sit, valde
  <lb/>dubito, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quod attinet ad posterius; ex occasione au<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tem prioris, quod est de invenienda <rs type="keyword">Catenaria</rs> ex data lege
  <lb/><rs type="keyword">virium centralium</rs> ad centrum finit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tendentium,
    <lb/>monere Te debeo, ut <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><del/> ansam de Te trium<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>phandi eripias corrigendo errorem qui est in <rs type="biblio">Phoron.</rs> <abbr>pag.</abbr>
  <lb/>46<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> et <abbr>pag.</abbr> 382<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> ubi dicis,<del/>
    <lb/><del/>si potenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint proportionales elementis Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, et ipsa<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <pb facs="1038152" n="3"/>
  <lb break="no"/>rum directiones concurrant ad punctum finit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, <rs type="keyword">Catena<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>riam</rs> esse hyperbolam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilateram, cujus centrum in centro
    <lb/>virium; quo<add>d</add><del/> hoc verum esse <add>non</add> possit<del/> vel ex eo
  <lb/>solo apparet, quod augendo distantiam centri usque in infini<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tum hyperbola <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilatera <add>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> tandem <add>evadit linea recta</add> deberet evadere Catenaria
  <lb/>vulgaris, et ex curva algebraica in casu particulari mutari in
  <lb/>Curvam transcendentem; jam vero quod curva transcendens sub
  <lb/>curva algebraica tanquam species sub genere comprehendi pos<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <lb break="no"/>sit,<del/> asserere non voles. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119291967">Fardellam</rs> jam ante plures
    <lb/>menses diem suum obiisse fortasse non ignorabis. <rs type="person">Petrus</rs> tuus<del/>
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> longo tempore mihi non amplius servit, ex quo scilicet <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <rs type="place">Patria</rs>,
    <lb/>quam post mortem <rs type="person">Patris</rs> inviseram, redux<del/> apud <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs>
  <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>orari coepi. Monialis aliqua ex monasterio <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Catharin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>se <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileensem</rs> esse dicit, mihi <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> cum panibus dulciariis misit
  <lb/>semel atque iterum, credens prima vice <add>se eas</add> mittere Tibi, cujus nomen
  <lb/>(male quidem expressum) litteris inscriptum erat; puto autem Te non
    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre laturum, quod munus<del/> <add>T</add>ibi destinatum<del/> ad me vel po<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tius ad <rs type="persons">Polenianos</rs>, quibus illud consumendum dederam, pervenerit.
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Junior Scheuchzerorum fratrum</rs>, amicus noster, quem Collegam
  <lb/>meum fore sperabam,<note type="comment"></note> injuriam (dent veniam verbo superi)<del/> passus
  <lb/>est non levem; concordibus suffragiis<del/> electus erat ab <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mis</hi></abbr>
    <lb/>et <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">mis</hi></abbr> <rs type="persons">Reformatoribus</rs> in locum Abbatis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104058412">Viali</rs>, qui (ut dicere
  <lb/>solent) jubilatus est <add>sed</add> ista electio <add>licet</add> probata <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Collegi<add>o</add> Sapientum,
    <lb/><del/>non delata <add>fuit</add> ad Senatum, id quod min<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> potentum et artes<del/>
    <lb/><del/><add>inimicorum</add> (ne dicam amicorum) nostrorum effecerunt. In ejus
  <lb/>locum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="persons">Reformatoribus</rs> et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Senatu <rs type="person">Pontedera</rs> quidam, ju<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <lb break="no"/>venis sed cliens<del/> Eminentissimi electus fuit cum
  <pb facs="1038153" n="4"/>
  <lb/>stipendio 200<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> florenorum. Canonicus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1158980426">Giacometti</rs> Professor noster <abbr>Phil.</abbr>
  <lb/><abbr>Mor.</abbr> quem ad sanam mentem rediturum non putabant (ita enim malefe<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>riatus erat, ut sibimet manus violentas intulerit) Professionem suam
  <lb/>nuper auspicatus est coram incredibili multitudine auditorum.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale.</salute> 
